{"tid":513090,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"近兩套拉打既動作設計越來越冇特色","createTime":"2017-12-29T07:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T14:08:00.000Z","uid":22898,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f747fa0d9ff84f301a97061bfe8339a5240f0c58","tid":513090,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"我講緊個打交風格<br />\n以前既拉打一睇動作都知知係邊個<br />\n<br />\n555既FIng手/爛仔交風格<br />\nkabuto 既被動型打法<br />\n電王唔同人唔同打法（桃太郎就尻沖、浦島太郞就乸型...）<br />\nW既腳膠打法<br />\nOoo就虎型<br />\nWizard詠春風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算年配角都係佢特色<br />\n<br />\nBirth既摔角打法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMetor既功夫<br />\n<br />\n但係最近幾套既拉打動作冇曬個人特色<br />\n睇到Build個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拳擊手</span></span>變身之後都係用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劍</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBuild 打個陣又係冇特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2218da1ddf0e65bde8bfb7553a4300b65b27ba0b","tid":513090,"uid":96829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"淨係記得555每次變強既時候<br />\n對面無論點打佢都唔郁，然後一拳一拳咁打番怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966bdee4dbb8d426f246afeee2d5496eaa33f6c8","tid":513090,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"龍騎初期真司果種雞手鴨腳嘅打法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有王蛇勁有霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a71f5577de7726a3b801618ed469c1a979e5a2","tid":513090,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q